<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 01:05:57 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>公布裁员和减产计划后，日产股价暴跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/nissan-shares-slump-after-unveiling-plan-cut-jobs-production-2024-11-08/</link><description>日产汽车 (Nissan Motor) 周五在东京交易中股价下跌 10%，此前该公司前一天表示，由于中国和美国的销售陷入困境，将裁员 9,000 人，并削减全球 20% 的产能。</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 00:45:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/nissan-shares-slump-after-unveiling-plan-cut-jobs-production-2024-11-08/</guid></item><item><title>中国新型隐形战斗机将成为中国最大航展的焦点</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/new-chinese-stealth-fighter-take-centre-stage-chinas-biggest-air-show-2024-11-08/</link><description>中国新型J-35A隐形战斗机将于下周在中国最大的民用和军用航空展上首次亮相，这是北京两年一度的盛会，展示其不断发展的航空航天工业。</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 00:05:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/new-chinese-stealth-fighter-take-centre-stage-chinas-biggest-air-show-2024-11-08/</guid></item><item><title>防晒霜制造商 Edgewell 希望在特朗普关税上调之前锁定中国化学品供应</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/sunscreen-maker-edgewell-looks-lock-chinese-chemicals-supply-ahead-trump-tariff-2024-11-07/</link><description>美国防晒霜制造商 Edgewell Personal Care 首席运营官丹·沙利文 (Dan Sullivan) 告诉路透社，该公司将寻求与来自中国的化学品签订新的两到三年期合同，因为如果当选总统唐纳德·特朗普兑现其竞选承诺，该公司预计关税将“有意义”上调星期四。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 22:39:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/sunscreen-maker-edgewell-looks-lock-chinese-chemicals-supply-ahead-trump-tariff-2024-11-07/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：鲍威尔暗示美联储仍处于宽松轨道，“风险继续”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-pix-graphic-2024-11-07/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 21:47:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-pix-graphic-2024-11-07/</guid></item><item><title>普京称中国是俄罗斯的盟友并支持其在台湾问题上的立场</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/putin-says-china-is-russias-ally-backs-its-stance-taiwan-2024-11-07/</link><description>俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京周四将中国描述为俄罗斯的盟友，并大力支持北京对台湾的主权主张，同时表示没有任何国家可以担心深化中俄合作。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 20:22:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/putin-says-china-is-russias-ally-backs-its-stance-taiwan-2024-11-07/</guid></item><item><title>普京暗示俄罗斯可能与朝鲜举行军事演习</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/putin-says-partnership-deal-with-north-korea-is-sign-stability-region-2024-11-07/</link><description>俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京周四表示，俄罗斯可以与朝鲜举行军事演习。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 19:57:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/putin-says-partnership-deal-with-north-korea-is-sign-stability-region-2024-11-07/</guid></item><item><title>史蒂文·马登因特朗普领导下的关税担忧而减少从中国采购</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/steven-madden-cut-sourcing-china-tariff-worries-under-trump-2024-11-07/</link><description>史蒂文·马登(Steven Madden)高管周四表示，在唐纳德·特朗普(Donald Trump)赢得美国总统大选后，该公司正在迅速将产品采购从中国转移到其他国家。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 16:44:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/steven-madden-cut-sourcing-china-tariff-worries-under-trump-2024-11-07/</guid></item><item><title>中国火星车帮助寻找古代火星海岸线的证据</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/space/chinese-rover-helps-find-evidence-ancient-martian-shoreline-2024-11-07/</link><description>在中国祝融号火星车的帮助下，科学家们收集到了新的证据，证明火星在数十亿年前曾是海洋的家园，与今天干燥荒凉的世界相去甚远。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 16:03:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/space/chinese-rover-helps-find-evidence-ancient-martian-shoreline-2024-11-07/</guid></item><item><title>中国上市电视制造商因付款问题暂停俄罗斯工厂的生产</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/china-listed-tv-maker-halts-work-russian-factory-over-payment-issues-2024-11-07/</link><description>一家在中国上市的飞利浦、夏普和索尼电视机制造商周四告诉路透社，由于与外国供应商的备件付款问题，该工厂已停止其位于圣彼得堡附近的俄罗斯工厂的生产。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 15:54:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/china-listed-tv-maker-halts-work-russian-factory-over-payment-issues-2024-11-07/</guid></item><item><title>美国银行将从特朗普领导下的宽松资本和合并政策中获益</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/us-banks-gain-looser-capital-merger-policies-under-trump-2024-11-07/</link><description>行业专家和分析师表示，随着前总统唐纳德·特朗普重返白宫，共和党监管机构预计将放宽资本规则和合并审批，银行业预计将赢得巨大胜利。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 15:38:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/us-banks-gain-looser-capital-merger-policies-under-trump-2024-11-07/</guid></item><item><title>意大利削减汽车行业支持以避免资助中国制造的汽车</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/italy-cuts-automotive-industry-support-avoid-funding-cars-made-china-2024-11-07/</link><description>意大利经济部长周四表示，意大利政府计划削减此前用于支持该国汽车工业的资金，以避免资助中国制造的汽车。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 14:12:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/italy-cuts-automotive-industry-support-avoid-funding-cars-made-china-2024-11-07/</guid></item><item><title>奥迪在中国推出无四环标志的新电动汽车品牌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/audi-unveils-new-ev-brand-china-without-four-ring-logo-2024-11-07/</link><description>奥迪周四在中国推出了一个新的电动汽车品牌，该品牌的汽车将仅使用奥迪名称，而不是其标志性的四环标志，此举旨在吸引全球最大汽车市场的年轻客户。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 13:33:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/audi-unveils-new-ev-brand-china-without-four-ring-logo-2024-11-07/</guid></item><item><title>德国逮捕涉嫌向中国提供军事情报的美国公民</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/germany-arrests-us-citizen-suspected-offering-military-intel-china-2024-11-07/</link><description>德国联邦检察官办公室周四在一份声明中表示，德国逮捕了一名涉嫌向中国提供美国军方情报的美国公民，这些情报是他在为驻德部队工作时获得的。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 13:00:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/germany-arrests-us-citizen-suspected-offering-military-intel-china-2024-11-07/</guid></item><item><title>塔塔钢铁首席执行官表示，长期从中国进口可能会影响印度钢铁行业的投资</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/prolonged-chinese-imports-may-hit-indian-steel-industrys-investments-tata-steel-2024-11-07/</link><description>塔塔钢铁公司首席执行官周四对路透表示，印度从中国进口的钢铁价格“不公平”，长期发货可能会损害国内钢铁行业的投资计划。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 12:53:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/prolonged-chinese-imports-may-hit-indian-steel-industrys-investments-tata-steel-2024-11-07/</guid></item><item><title>独家：联合利华、宝洁公司面临特朗普威胁对墨西哥征收关税的风险</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/unilever-procter-gamble-face-risk-trumps-threatened-mexico-tariffs-2024-11-07/</link><description>路透社独家看到的数据显示，如果美国当选总统唐纳德·特朗普继续威胁对墨西哥征收关税，宝洁和联合利华等大型包装商品公司将面临风险。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 12:48:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/unilever-procter-gamble-face-risk-trumps-threatened-mexico-tariffs-2024-11-07/</guid></item></channel></rss>